title: Pictured Rocks National Lakeshore: NPS Focus
body: NPS Focus         Experience Your America NPS photo  NPS Focus is an on-line digital library and research station.   It offers a growing collection including thousands of images, documents, drawings, and maps about the cultural and natural resources maintained by the National Park Service.   Please visit http://npsfocus.nps.gov/ to find digital and other information resources by and about the National Park Service.
